    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1910-06-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1910-06-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="495"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d495">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Sherrill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-06-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 1, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>For immediate communication to the Government to which you are accredited and for
                    repetition to Petropolis for corresponding action.</p>
                <p>I shall to-day hand the following aide-mémoire to the representatives of Ecuador
                    and Peru, and shall instruct our representatives at Quito and Lima to make
                    strong representations in the same sense to the two Governments, since the time
                    is too short for consultation and since, in any case, I feel sure that this
                    faithfully represents the views held also by the Governments of the Argentine
                    Republic and of Brazil, which have doubtless taken similar steps.<note n="3"
                        xml:id="d495fn3">Aide-mémoire, supra, June 1.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Knox.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
